Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.82,0:00:07.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live in a world of peace\NWithout conflict, like the one I dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.40,0:00:20.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be patient any longer\NThere are things I must say
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.33,0:00:23.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At the evening bus stop\Non the way home
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.49,0:00:26.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I Wave to those sunken shoulders,\NBye Bye Bye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.09,0:00:32.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Got to show your Fighting Pose, Oh! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.14,0:00:38.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That world I dreamed of\NIs peaceful every day, without any conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:40.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality,\Nthere are troubles every day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:44.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes I regret,\Nthese Rolling days
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.73,0:00:55.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lies probably have little meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.59,0:01:02.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,~All my loving\NOtherwise, how can I go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:09.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Sweet Love I dreamed of\NWhere lovers search for a hideaway
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.48,0:01:12.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality,\Nthe days we can't meet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:16.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go on; but we still believe,\Nthese Rolling days
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.68,0:01:25.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We may stumble, but Way to go!!\NYeah!! Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.76,0:01:28.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A mud-caked Rolling star!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:39.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was Mabashi's Spiritual Pressure\Nthat disappeared…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.40,0:01:43.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is pretty good…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.70,0:01:46.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now then,\Nthat person hiding over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:49.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it about time you came out?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.92,0:01:56.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:02:00.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to copy you and\Nhide my Spiritual Pressure…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.84,0:02:05.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you hide\Nyour Spiritual Pressure,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.67,0:02:10.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,anyone could find you\Nif you're that bloodthirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.83,0:02:12.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:16.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was searching for Ichinose…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.57,0:02:18.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:23.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? His Spiritual Pressure\Ndisappeared long ago…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:27.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you suppose\None of your allies did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.82,0:02:30.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm… What a waste…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:34.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped, then.\NI'll settle for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:39.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to make you pay\Nfor embarrassing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:44.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well… You underestimate me…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:52.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, fine…\NIt's my job…to erase Captains…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.32,0:03:07.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Baura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:18.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.20,0:03:22.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, is he the next opponent?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:23.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:26.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's not like the small fries\Nyou've been fighting until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.59,0:03:30.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's a captain of\Nthe Thirteen Court Guard Squads.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:34.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. It seems like\NI'll have fun today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:39.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the doll that you use?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:42.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My doll Baura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:47.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:49.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.76,0:03:52.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking that the Bounts\Nare really interesting indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.13,0:03:57.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know\Nthe source of your power?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:04.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It comes from Soul Society's\Nancient technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:07.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:10.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was a technology that\Nwas deemed dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.55,0:04:14.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and sealed away because\Nof a single accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.97,0:04:21.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How regretful…\NEven I don't have any complete data left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:23.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:25.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:29.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to be\Nmy research subjects?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:32.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:34.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, in the beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:37.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I never cared about the Bounts, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:41.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I became interested when\NI was looking at various data.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:45.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to do…\Nmy own research.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:50.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. I'll try to make it\Nas painless as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:56.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll even forget that you used me\Nto return that Quincy's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:00.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.35,0:05:01.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:06.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Our goal is the destruction\Nof Seireitei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:10.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To do that,\NI must remove those in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:11.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Baura!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.23,0:05:13.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:17.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My, my… Oh well…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:19.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:23.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to make you regret that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:25.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's nice Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:29.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't matter how strong\Nyour Spiritual Pressure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:32.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've received reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:33.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I recall correctly…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:36.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're a mole, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:40.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can only appear from\Nlarge surfaces like the ground or walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:44.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To try that on me in\Nthe World of the Living is one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:46.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but it's pointless here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:48.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tear him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:51.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ashisogijizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:05:58.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now then…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:00.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:02.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:12.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:18.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I never heard about…this ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:21.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:30.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:46.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You barely dodged that…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:48.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you…!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:50.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you know…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:54.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We Bounts have gotten stronger\Nby absorbing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:59.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,large quantities of high-quality reishi\Nsince coming to Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:05.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The ground isn't the only thing\Nthat’s Baura's space now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:10.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This sky, which is filled with reishi,\Nis all Baura's space!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:13.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's nowhere for you to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:18.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You call yourself a captain,\Nbut this is it…?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:20.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How boring…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:24.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:27.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The elevation of a Soul Reaper captain's\NSpiritual Pressure…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:29.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone fight a Bount?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:34.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That temporary fight amongst\NSoul Reapers
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:35.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,was also the work of the Bounts…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:41.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Curse those Bounts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.09,0:07:52.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.13,0:08:01.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My, my…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:03.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you do that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:11.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez…\NHow annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.53,0:08:19.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You have an amusing body…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:22.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!\NYou're just an experiment subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.84,0:08:25.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:29.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to make\Nyou shut up, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.49,0:08:31.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Baura!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:33.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.13,0:08:43.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think that\NI'll fall for the same trick twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:49.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I would have brought Nemu\Nif I knew this was the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.27,0:08:52.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It would have saved me\Na lot of trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:54.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,if I had used her as a decoy…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:09:02.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He always hides himself in\Nan alternate space when he's moving…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:04.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But he always shows himself\Nwhen he attacks
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:07.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and engulfs everything around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:09.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In that case…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.93,0:09:16.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This place is just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,0:09:18.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:22.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bount!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.99,0:09:34.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I found you, Bount!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:40.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When you appear from\Nan alternate space,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.53,0:09:44.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you have to swallow everything\Nin your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:49.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With this many obstacles\Nfloating in the air,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.43,0:09:52.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can sense your movements!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.88,0:09:53.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,0:09:56.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tear him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:58.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ashisogijizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:02.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:06.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:16.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty good…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:22.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Humph! It seems that\Nit was a bit shallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.94,0:10:24.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:26.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fine…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:29.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I've come this far,\NI can finish you off easily afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:33.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops, as an experiment subject,\NI can't finish you off…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:37.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to keep you\Nsomewhat alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:41.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will it go that well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.29,0:10:42.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:46.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This world is full of reishi.\NIt's a problem if you forget
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.59,0:10:50.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that we Bounts are invincible here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:54.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This power…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:59.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's like the reishi subordination\Nof that Quincy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.19,0:11:05.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We Bounts absorb reishi like this\Nto heal our wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.26,0:11:10.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, it doesn't matter\Nhow many times your attacks hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:12.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sooner or later,\Nyou'll run out of spiritual power
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:15.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and you'll be the one lying here\Nface down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.49,0:11:18.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.31,0:11:27.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the one who'll be lying\Nface down?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.73,0:11:32.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ashisogijizo paralyzes the limbs\Nof whomever it cuts…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:39.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It only cuts off the signals\Nfrom the brain to move limbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:41.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Movement is the only thing\Nit takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:47.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike anesthesia,\Nthe pain doesn't go away at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:49.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.61,0:11:50.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.93,0:11:58.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that Ashisogijizo's power\Nis good against Bounts…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:01.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With this power,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:04.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,it doesn't matter how much\Nyou recover by absorbing reishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:08.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is a new discovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:12.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, we'll continue this\Nat the research facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:15.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Baura…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:16.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:18.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:20.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:22.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:25.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:45.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:48.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But Ashisogijizo's effect won't wear off,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:51.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,no matter how far apart we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:54.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think that you can get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.91,0:13:03.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.31,0:13:04.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:07.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I just absorbed\Na large amount of reishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:10.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,These wounds will soon heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:18.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But his zanpakuto's effect\Nis remaining…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.01,0:13:21.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Curse that Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:25.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't disappear here…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.52,0:13:27.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Baura, counter attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.44,0:13:28.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:32.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just you watch, Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:41.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now then…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:44.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how long it'll take for him\Nto come after me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:47.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,when he senses\Nmy Spiritual Pressure…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:49.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:55.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You were pretty slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:58.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought…\Nyou would come this quickly…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.34,0:14:00.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm… That's a good expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:06.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to finish this all at once\Nas soon as you appeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:08.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm glad that I held back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:11.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to take\Na good look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:13.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How did you find my location?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.89,0:14:20.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My, my. Oh well…\NI'll tell you if you insist…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:22.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'd received a report that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:24.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,when the lieutenant of\NSquad 10 fought you…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:29.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She was able to track your whereabouts\Nusing the Kakushitsuijaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:34.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, as long as I have\Nyour Spiritual Pressure data…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:39.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can track you even if you hide\Nin an alternate space.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:43.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And Ichigo Kurosaki chased you\Nusing a mod soul
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:47.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,which could sense\NBount Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:52.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So I also developed something\Nlike this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:54.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:57.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:15:02.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This sensor doesn't function\Nwithout the proper data.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:07.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell the locations\Nof all the Bounts, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:09.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,your data has already been input.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:12.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was very tough to receive information
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:14.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,from those who returned from\Nthe World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:16.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With that last battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.83,0:15:21.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've made the final adjustments to\Nyour Spiritual Pressure record.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.53,0:15:25.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Were you targeting me from\Nthe beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:27.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that it was\Na coincidence
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.91,0:15:30.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that you met me in Seireitei,\Nas wide as this place is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:34.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your body, which has aged\Nfrom absorbing souls,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:37.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,makes for\Na great experiment subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:39.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:42.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's enough talk…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.53,0:15:46.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to my research room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:51.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be able to find out more things\Nabout Bounts if I study you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:55.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:59.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your Spiritual Pressure is\Ncompletely recorded in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.04,0:16:08.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the one who's cornered.\NIt's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.59,0:16:10.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Baura!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:12.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.81,0:16:13.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:16.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Byakurai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:19.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is the absorbed spiritual power\Nof the Soul Reapers
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:21.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,who attacked us before now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:40.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.58,0:16:47.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought that\Nit could move this fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:48.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Baura!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:49.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:00.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:04.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I sense a Bount!\NSomeone is fighting a Bount!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:05.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.06,0:17:06.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:08.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Around that big building!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:10.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shishinro, Repentance Cell, huh--?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.97,0:17:11.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:13.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.24,0:17:26.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're just trading blows…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:33.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You Bount…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:36.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait for you to revive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:40.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to finish this before\Nyou inject yourself with that drug!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:42.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Baura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:44.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:46.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:49.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting cocky for\Nan experiment subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.07,0:17:51.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:53.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bankai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:54.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:02.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Konjiki Ashisogijizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.42,0:18:09.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Konjiki Ashisogijizo turns\Na deadly poison made from my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:11.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,into mist and scatters it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:13.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's nowhere for you to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.85,0:18:15.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A poison…you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:20.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Baura! Suck in the poison!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:22.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.38,0:18:30.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Baura! I'm going to give you\Nall my spiritual power!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:35.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'm going to suck\Neverything in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:36.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get cocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:41.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to keep you alive\Nand make you my experiment subject,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.25,0:18:42.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.73,0:18:45.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're finished here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:51.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:55.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I broke my tribe's laws
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:58.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and sucked tens of thousands\Nof human souls…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:19:01.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I got this body as a result…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.02,0:19:05.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Despite that, I never stopped\Ntrying to suck more souls
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.55,0:19:07.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,in order to increase my powers…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.39,0:19:11.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All for the sake of becoming\Nthe leader of the Bounts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:13.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not Kariya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:26.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I am most worthy of leading\Nthe Bounts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.38,0:19:32.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder about that. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:35.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Konjiki Ashisogijizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:44.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.80,0:19:54.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:57.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Konjiki Ashisogijizo…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:03.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who's having such a flashy fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:16.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I told you that\Nthere's nowhere to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.46,0:20:18.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Baura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:19.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Baura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:32.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like you had the ambition\Nto become the leader of the Bounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.63,0:20:35.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like\Nyou won't be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.41,0:20:39.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! I'll give you\NBount information…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:42.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.43,0:20:44.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I… I… I…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:50.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no longer interested in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.05,0:20:53.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.13,0:21:04.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aww… The poison has already spread\Nthroughout his system…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:07.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:10.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like I wasted my time…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:13.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've used up all the hojiku-zai\NI had on hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.69,0:21:16.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll return to the Department\Nof Research and Development.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.48,0:21:23.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.25,0:21:25.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anyone good\Naround here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:27.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:28.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nieder!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:29.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.56,0:21:46.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Quincy boy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.62,0:22:16.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You always lament on\Nhow boring this town is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.29,0:22:20.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,…Searching for a place in the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.87,0:22:25.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The melody you hum is that\Nrusty, same old song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.55,0:22:29.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,…Rejecting any new song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.69,0:22:38.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're anxious because somewhere\Nin your heart, you believe in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.68,0:22:40.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Baby, it's you;
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.78,0:22:48.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That pain will eventually become\Na memory
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.17,0:22:50.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.17,0:22:57.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think, just feel,\Nlet your whole body tremble;
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.77,0:22:59.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,future is you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.73,0:23:01.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Baby, it's me;
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.88,0:23:09.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're never alone, I'm right here
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.07,0:23:11.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We should be as one;
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.15,0:23:14.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you stumble, I don’t mind
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.94,0:23:21.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to tell you now\Nabout the thing called love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.29,0:23:26.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida, sorry to interrupt you\Nwhile you're fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.91,0:23:28.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but could you do something\Nabout that uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.42,0:23:29.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.68,0:23:31.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is the ancient Quincy uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.99,0:23:34.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This fashion sense feels like\Na breath of great history.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.55,0:23:36.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand\Nhow fabulous it is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.85,0:23:38.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I try to but…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.01,0:23:49.98,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers\NGolden after these messages!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.05,0:23:51.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,llustrated guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.31,0:23:52.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Golden!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.64,0:23:54.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hitsugaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.26,0:23:56.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.97,0:23:59.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Bounts have invaded the court,\Nhaven't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.05,0:24:03.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where should Squad 3 be positioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.37,0:24:06.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. I forgot to contact you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.11,0:24:06.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.62,0:24:09.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Matsumoto, really…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.55,0:24:14.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well. Kira…Squad 3 is\Nto guard the Hakuto Gate…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.24,0:24:15.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.29,0:24:17.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any other squads\Nyou forgot, are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.93,0:24:19.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.03,0:24:28.01,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Boy!